# Deployment

## Requirements

- `git`
- `docker` and `docker-compose`
- `mise` or `just` (for convenience)

## Setup

```bash
git clone git@gitlab.tu-clausthal.de:ifi-data/api.git
cd api/draft
mise trust
mise install
just start
```

